channel.title: Someone Help!
channel.description:
I posted a topic about this earlier, but nobody replied, and i really need help :( When i press run for my server it says its online, bu when i log in, it stays at a black screen, then after about 20 seconds, it says, connection lost, logs me out, and my accoutn is still logged on. someone help! this is what the [i]run[/i] file says:
[i]- Project Czar - .. Online! Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "217 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:2092) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:33) [/i]

item.title: Someone Help!
item.dc:creator: @draggon67 draggon67
item.description:
@draggon67 wrote:

YES thank you guys soooo much! it was in my autospawn, i put the npc id 217 and it looked right, but i just deleted it and it worked. hmm. thanks sooo much guys!
